examples.en: He propped his bike against a tree.
A tree was propped up by iron stays.
He propped himself against the door.
She propped the rake against a tree.
The shipbuilding industry had to be propped up with government money.
There was a ladder propped up against the wall.
We propped the shed's roof with poles.
She propped the mirror against her handbag and began to paint her lips.
